---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Services — Mangrove" description="From a focused audit to a full transformation — Mangrove's operational consulting services scale to what your business needs.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="section-label">Services</p>
      <h1>Three ways to work with us</h1>
      <p>From a focused project to a 12-month partnership — all designed to make your business easier to run.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Audit -->
      <div style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: var(--primary); background: var(--bg-alt); padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 4px;">Audit</span>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Essential Ecosystem Audit</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">A focused review of your key business systems — where the friction is, what's costing you time, and the quickest wins to fix it fast.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary);">$3,900<span style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted);">/mo</span></div>
            <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">for 2 months, then $350/mo</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary);">$12,000<span style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted);">/yr</span></div>
            <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">$350/mo for 12 months</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem 2rem; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Business ecosystem audit</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Pain point analysis</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Ecosystem audit report</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Quick wins you can do in 30 mins</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Strategic recommendations</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 10 implementation credits</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 12 months support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex;">Book an Ecosystem Audit →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Transformation -->
      <div style="background: var(--bg-alt); border: 2px solid var(--primary); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <div style="display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 0.75rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <span style="font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 700; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; color: #fff; background: var(--primary); padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem; border-radius: 4px;">Most popular</span>
        </div>
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Ecosystem Transformation</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Broader operational improvement across your whole business. We map, redesign and implement the systems and processes that actually run the place.</p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 1.75rem;">
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary);">$9,700<span style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted);">/mo</span></div>
            <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">for 2 months, then $550/mo</div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div style="font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--primary);">$26,000<span style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--text-muted);">/yr</span></div>
            <div style="font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--text-muted);">$550/mo for 12 months</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem 2rem; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Full ecosystem audit</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Ecosystem strategy</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Pain point analysis</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 24 implementation credits</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Ecosystem audit report</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> 12 months support</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="display: inline-flex;">Start a Transformation →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Advisory -->
      <div style="background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">Ecosystem Advisory</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Ongoing access to strategic input and operational guidance — for when you need a thinking partner, not just a do-er.</p>
        <ul style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0.6rem 2rem; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 2rem; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--text-muted);">
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Quarterly business reviews</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Strategic advice & second opinions</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Improvement prioritisation</li>
          <li style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 0.5rem;"><span style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 700;">✓</span> Priority support</li>
        </ul>
        <div style="font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">From $900/month</div>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary" style="display: inline-flex;">Talk to Us →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-band">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Not sure where to start?</h2>
      <p>Most engagements begin with a free consultation. Let's figure it out together.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book a Free Consultation →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
